      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been professionally addressed with subframe reinforcement plates and features upgraded Bilstein PSS10 coilover suspension for optimized damping and roll center geometry. Every aspect of the drivetrain remains in peak mechanical synchronization, with a comprehensive service history detailing recent valve adjustments and rod bearing prophylaxis. The exterior maintains a concours-level finish with zero rock chips or clear coat failure, while the interior leather and trim remain in showroom state. A truly turnkey performance machine for the serious enthusiast.",
